---
title: Blueberry-BBQ Chicken Tenders with Roasted Potatoes and Spinach Salad
description: Sometimes the best things in life are unexpected, like this delicious combination of blueberry jam and BBQ sauce. This pairing adds a little something special to this chicken dinner, which is completed with roasted potatoes and crunchy spinach salad.
